doc.after: Airbus Helicopters then named Eurocopter Group was formed in 1992 through the merger of the helicopter divisions of A rospatiale and Daimler Benz Aerospace AG DASA The company s heritage traces back to Bl riot and Lior et Olivier in France and to Messerschmitt and Focke Wulf in Germany 3
